An android application for downloading and displaying mountain bike trail reports.

<a href="https://bitbucket.org/ande3577/mtb-trail-report/wiki/Home">Project Page</a>

<a href="http://www.morcmtb.org/morcpages/cond1.htm">Trail Conditions Explained</a>

Please obey all trail closures and do not ride in conditions that will cause damage to the trail.
<a href="http://www.morcmtb.org/forums/trailconditions.php#Closed">Why are trails Closed</a>

This project is currently in beta, not all functionality may be completely implemented.  Please report issues on any problems you find.  Include the make/model and firmware revision of your phone.
<a href="https://bitbucket.org/ande3577/mtb-trail-report/issues?status=new&status=open">Issue Tracker</a>

This project is not affiliated with MORC, or any other website or trail manager.  Do not contact any website provider with 
questions or issues with this application.  The author of this application is not responsible for any inaccurate or out of 
date information that may be present in trail reports, including any injuries or damages that may occur as a result of
riding a trail in unsafe conditions.  The author is also not responsible for any vulgarity or offensive language or images.

